ziale Evolution sowie die Geschäftsmodelle der Konsumgüterindustrie und bahnt damit der Soziologie, den Kulturwissenschaften sowie der Semiotik und Ökonomik einen gemeinsamen Zugang zu einem Interessengebiet, das bisher mit widersprüchlichen Paradigmen bearbeitet wurde.  afunded by Swiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aConsumer behaviorxSocial aspects. 0aConsumption (Economics). 0aEconomicsxSociological aspects. 0aSocial sciences (General). 4aEvolution. 4aGesellschaft. 4aIndustrie. 4aKommunikation. 4aKultur. 4aKultursoziologie. 4aKulturtheorie. 4aMainstream. 4aMarken. 4aPostmoderne. 4aSoziologie. 4aStil. 4aWirtschaft. 4aWirtschaftswissenschaft. 4aÖkonomik. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aBranding.  aCommunication.  aCultural Theory.  aCulture.  aEconomics.  aEconomy.  aEvolution.  aIndustry.  aMainstream.  aPostmodernism.  aSociety.  aSociology of Culture.  aSociology.  aStyle.2 aSwiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology, Education, Psychology 2020z9783110704549oZDB-23-SEW0 cprintz978383764909340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839449097?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839449097zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn